{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732540/extras/\u5173\u4e8e\u5267\u60c5-\u82f1\u8bed.png?t=1737265910\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u300cPersisting in kindness, some people say it is absurd and dismiss it; But in the Realm where wedge energy and will intertwine, it brought us you and rally you.\u300d </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a kind soul that comes to the realm, begins a journey of redemption in the realm of the raging tide of black beasts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300cWhen greed and violence destroy the nameless flower, we know why the Dawn Dew comes......\u300d</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the process of continuous progress, discover the history of the realm and uncover the truth of the Black beast tide.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732540/extras/\u5f00\u573a\u5730600-250.gif?t=1737265910\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732540/extras/\u5bcc\u6709\u63a2\u7d22\u6027\u7684\u573a\u666f-\u82f1\u8bed.png?t=1737265910\" />Explore box style maps with designs, collect various resources in the scene, and make yourself stronger.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732540/extras/\u6361\u5b9d\u7bb1600-250.gif?t=1737265910\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't worry about boring lost time. You have clear map guidance and can teleport at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732540/extras/\u4f7f\u7528\u591a\u79cd\u624b\u6bb5\u6218\u6597-\u82f1\u8bed.png?t=1737265910\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Free to form your combat style </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect nearly a hundred skills, experiences, prop